# Telly

A super performance HDHomeRun transcoding server

## Installation

```ruby
go get -t -d -v ./...
go install 
go build main/telly.go
./telly
```

And then execute:

    $ open localhost:8888

## Configs

You can specify following configs as ENV variables

HDHOMERUN_HOST - HDHomeRun IP (Default: 10.0.1.31)

FFMPEG_PATH - Path to ffmpag (Default: /usr/local/bin/ffmpeg)

PORT - Port to run webserver on (Default: 8888)

